# Frontend Patterns

## State & Data Fetching

- All API calls go through RTK Query in `src/redux/api/`. Never use raw `fetch` or `axios` in components.
- State slices live in `src/redux/reducers/`.
- Use existing hooks (`useAppSelector`, `useAppDispatch`, `usePermissions`).

## Components

- Functional components only. No class components.
- UI primitives are in `src/elements/ui/` (shadcn-style). Use them instead of raw HTML.
- Layouts and shared chrome are in `src/components/layouts/`.

## i18n

- All user-facing strings must use `t("key")` from `useTranslation()`.
- Keys are flat dot-notation: `sidebar.dashboard`, `auth.login_title`, `common.save`.
- Translations live in `src/locales/{en,ar,es}/translation.json`.
- Arabic is RTL — handled by `I18nProvider` and `layoutSlice.isRTL`.

## Routing

- App Router in `src/app/`. Authenticated pages under `(mainLayout)/`.
- Guards: `RoleGuard` (RBAC), `FeatureGuard` (Baileys restrictions), `SubscriptionGuard`.
